Investing is my MOST important bill.

Nothing else comes even close.

Pay. Yourself. First. 👏
Returns start slow, but end big. In order to reach the big gains, you’ve gotta be patient in the beginning and allow the compounding interest do its thing 💯

node.text:
Be careful selling your future income to someone else! Sure, there are times when taking on debt could work in your favor (taking out a home loan, business loan, etc) But I’d generally avoid selling your future income at all costs!

Protect your income so that you can get rich off of it yourself, NOT someone else!

#themarkethustle #stocks #investing #money #finance #invest

Enjoy your 20/30s by building good habits that will position you to enjoy the rest of your life as well. 💯🔥

#stocks #investing #money #finance #invest

Doesn’t matter how old you are, you’ll always wish you would have started earlier when you start to understand how investing works. Never fails. 😂

#stocks #investing #money
